# Step 5 – Restart FastAPI

Stop the server:

```text
Ctrl + C
```

Run:

```bash
uvicorn main:app --reload --host 0.0.0.0
```

The first time it runs, it will automatically create:

```text
blood_reports.db
```

inside your `backend` folder.

